keyMappings:
unmapAll
map ? showHelp
map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map d scrollPageDown
map u scrollPageUp
map h scrollLeft
map l scrollRight
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map B Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map H goBack
map L goForward
map J previousTab
map K nextTab
map <c-y> duplicateTab
map <c-m> toggleMuteTab
